Refer to [FSH-3039|https://support.atlassian.com/browse/FSH-3039].

{quote}
If you navigate to the repository location you want to add a watch to using the left-hand navigation, it does not change the location in the browser's Address Bar. The watches do not take any effect and it doesn't appear in the user's profile watches.

However, if you click the "Permalink" link prior to adding the watch, then the Address Bar gets updated, and you can add a watch successfully.
{quote}

Need to update the changeset-mail-*.ftl files as they have:

{noformat}
${siteurl}?dialog=${"/profile/showWatches.do"?url}
{noformat}

However /profile/showWatches.do should not be url encoded, as [https://extranet.atlassian.com/crucible/?dialog=%2Fprofile%2FshowWatches.do] will throw a "There is no action Mapped for namespace //profile" error 

Thus the templates should show:

{noformat}
${siteurl}?dialog=/profile/showWatches.do
{noformat}
